summary: Elaina is a Wood Elf from the lost Silver Elf tribe.  Pretty, with silver hair that seems to lighten and darken under different lighting. The name meaning for \"Elaina\" is \"sun ray, shining light\".
descriptionHtml:
Elaina is a Wood Elf from the lost \"Silver Elf\" tribe.  Pretty, with silver hair that seems to lighten and darken under different lighting.
 
BONUS: Appaloosa horse with Ornate silver saddle, Kantana \"Nodachi\" sword, Wonderous Armor & Daedric Bow of Terror all in the save if the mods listed below are used.

The name meaning for \"Elaina\" is \"sun ray, shining light\".
A LV-2 save in Riverwood at the start of the game. 

Five uploaded images to show what Elaina, her armor, bow, horse and saddle look like. 

Mods used for this save game. Face, body, horse, armor, weapons \"etc\"  may differ or be missing if you do not use the mods listed below. All the mods listed below can be found here on Nexus. A big thank you to each everyone of their creators.

My Type of Hair         ( use the Transparent version )
Better_Females_by_Bella
Then add bella Less_Make_up_Version
Calientes_Female_Body_Mod_BBE
Natural_Eyes
BlackLight Katana standalone
Triss Armor Retextured    (dark brotherhood version)
Shrouded Cowl-Hood Swap
Zira Retextured Horses
Ornate Saddles
author: celt43
